          <cite>— Head of SEO at a Top-50 US retailer</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <h2 id="vs-stacc">DeepCrawl vs theStacc</h2>
        <p>If you found this review by searching for "DeepCrawl alternative" or "DeepCrawl pricing", you are probably not the target customer. Lumar is built for SEO <em>teams</em> at brands above $100M revenue. If you are a marketer, founder, or agency owner, the better question is: <strong>do you need a crawler at all, or do you need an SEO system that publishes too?</strong></p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
