            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Pricing starts around $14,000 per year for the Corporate plan (500K URLs, 3 seats, 4 crawls/month). Enterprise tiers range from $30,000 to $80,000+ annually. There is no public self-serve tier and no monthly contract.</p></div></div>
