            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>DeepCrawl wins on scale (10M+ URLs, scheduling, team workflow, log file analysis). Screaming Frog wins on price and one-off audits. Most teams under 500K pages will be happier — and just as effective — with Screaming Frog.</p></div></div>
