            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes — Lumar renders JS at scale using a headless Chrome 124+ cluster. It is one of the very few crawlers that does this reliably above 1M URLs. JS rendering does roughly double the crawl time and the URL count toward your plan limit.</p></div></div>
